quran[339]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Nnan wid ur nessarem ara timlilit yidne£: \"a lemmer id ssersen lmalayek $uône$, ne$ nwala Mass nne$\"! Ni$ sme$wôen aîas iman nnsen, u ffuhrin aîas"
  25,22,"Ass ideg ara walin lmalayek, ur ippili wassen d abecceô ibe$wviyen, s lxiô. A d inin: d aêdid ur nepwazgar"
  25,23,"Nezzi $eô igiten nnsen, Nerra ten d a$ebbaô immebruzzâen"
  25,24,"Imawlan n Loennet, assen, di tnezdu$t akked trusi iufraren"
  25,25,"Ass ideg ara iceqqeq igenni s usigna, ideg ara d ssersen lmalayek, ta deffir ta"
  25,26,"tagelda, assen, tidep, i Uênin. D ass uwâiô i ijehliyen"
  25,27,"Ass ideg ara i$eéé umednus ifassen is, ad yini: \"a yamxix iw, a lemmer ddi$ d ubrid Umazan"
  25,28,"A tawa$it pwa$e$, a lemmer ur rri$ ara winnat d aêbib"
  25,29,"Ni$ itelf iyi seg usmekti i illan iusa yi d. Cciîan, i umdan, izga d axeddaâ"
  25,30,"Inna Umazan: \"a Mass iw! Ar ugdud iw, s tidep, Leqwôan agi d askeôfeé"
  25,31,"Akka, i yal nnbi, Nefka acengu seg ibe$wviyen. Iqadd Mass ik, i nnhaya akked usellek"
  25,32,"Nnan wid ijehlen: \"a lemmer i s d ssersen Leqwôan, deg yiwet n tikelt\"! Akka, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yis. Nesemderri t d idurra"
  25,33,"Ur ak d ppawin amedya, mebla ma Nuzen ak d tidep, akked ufesser amxallef"
  25,34,"Wid ara ipwafesren af udmawen nnsen, ar Loahennama, widak d at umkan n dir mavi, d at ubrid im$eôôeq mavi"
  25,35,"Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa, u Nerna $uôes gma s, Haôun, d am²âiwen"
  25,36,"Nenna: \"ôuêet ar ugdud i inekôen issekniyen nne£\". Nhudd iten qeccuc meccuc"
  25,37,"Agdud n Nuê, mi nekôen imazanen, Ne$ves iten, u Nerra ten d assekni i medden. Nhegga i imednas aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  25,38,"Âad, Tamud, At Öôas, u aîas isuta garasen"
  25,39,"I yal wa, Nefka imedyaten. Yal wa, Neôéa t wakali"
  25,40,"Ni$ âaddan $ef taddart i$ef id i$li ugeffur ageswaê. Day qqimen ur p walan ara? Xaîi, ur ssaramen ara tanekra"
  25,41,"Mi k walan, ppemsexxiôen kan fellak: \"day d wagi id Iuzen Öebbi, d Amazan"
  25,42,"Qôib i $ itlef seg iôebbiten nne$, lemmer ur neûbiô fellasen\". Deqqal ad éôen mara walin aâaqeb, anwa i innetlafen, kteô, seg ubrid"
  25,43,"Twalav win i irran lhawiyya s d ôebbi s? Day ad as tiliv, keçç, d awkil"
  25,44,"Day t$ilev tegwti, segsen, sellen ne$ fehmen? Nitni am lmal kan, aâer $elben ten akken nnetlafen seg ubrid"
  25,45,"Ma twalav Mass ik, amek id Ifka tili? Lemmer i S ihwi, Irra p d tusbiî. D$a Nefka yas itij d ppbut"
  25,46,"Sinna, Njebd ip id $uône£, ajbad isehlen"
  25,47,"D Neppa i wen Irran iv d aceîîiv, ives d areyyeê, u Irra ass d tanekra"
  25,48,"D Neppa i wen d Iuznen avu, d abecceô s uêunu S. Nessers ed, seg igenni, aman iûfan"
  25,49,"iwakken a Neêyu yissen tamurt immuten; a Nessew yissen aîas seg wid id Nexleq n lmal, akked imdanen"
  25,50,"Ni$ Nfeôq iten garasen, iwakken a d mmektin. Tegwti n yimdanen ugin; atnan kan di tijehli"
  25,51,"Lemmer i £ ihwi, yili Nuzen aneddaô, i yal tamdint"
  25,52,"Ur ppa$ awal i ijehliyen. Nna$ iten yis, amennu$ ameqwôan"
  25,53,"D Neppa i Issemfaôaqen sin ilellen, yiwen êlaw, d aéidan, wayev ôéag, d ameô$an. Irra, garasen, agadir, aêdid ur nepwazgar"
  25,54,"D Neppa i Ixelqen amdan seg waman. Ifka yas laâmum, lexwal. Mass ik Izga d Win Izemren"
  25,55,"La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen ur ten inefâan, ur ten ivuôôen. Ajehli, ar loiha n Mass is, izga d win issefôa$en"
  25,56,"Nuzen ik id kan, i ubecceô d uneddeô"
  25,57,"Ini: \"ur awen ssutre$, $ef waya, kra n teqdiât. Ssutre$ kan, i win ib$an, ad ia$ abrid $eô Mass is"
  25,58,Ppkel $ef Umuddir ur Nepmeppat. Sbuccaâ iT s ccekôan. Iqadd i tussna ibekkaven n imdanen iS
  25,59,"I Ixelqen tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan. Sinna, Aênin Iâannec af usgeld. Steqsi w iT issnen"
  25,60,"Ma pwanecden: \"knut i Uênin\"! A d rren: \"d acu T Uênin? Day a neknu i w ara $ d tamôev\"? D a$unfu i sen irna"
  25,61,"Ad Iôqu Win Irran itran deg igenni. Irna degs, lefnaô, akked waggur bu tziri"
  25,62,"D Neppa i Irran iv akked wass mestebâan, i win ib$an ad ismekti, ne$ ib$an ad isnemmer"
  25,63,"Ixdimen n Uênin, i ileêêun di tmurt di lehna, ma numren ten at war tussna, qqaôen: \"tifrat"
  25,64,"I ippaâwazen i Mass nnsen, knan ne$ bedden"
  25,65,"I iqqaôen: \"a Mass nne$! Veôôef segne$ aâaqeb n Loahennama. Ih, aâaqeb is ipwaêeppem"
  25,66,"Neppat, s tidep, d tadirant, i tnezdu$t akked i$imi"
  25,67,"Wid, ma seôôfen, ur veggiâen, ur pcuêêun: igi iwulmen atan garasen"
  25,68,"Wid ur nenâaô ôebbi nniven, ar tama n Öebbi. Ur neqqen amdan, d ayen Igdel Öebbi, siwa $ef tidep. Ur zennun. Win ixedmen ayagi, ibbwi ibekkaven"
  25,69,"Ad ippuâaqeb berdayen, ass n tnekra. Ad iwekkeô d imdelli"
  25,70,"siwa win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I wigi, ad Inûef Öebbi tucmitin nnsen, s yise$iyen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  25,71,"Win isteôoâen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ihi, iutub Öebbi s ppuba n tidep"
  25,72,"Wid ur ncehhed ccada n rrya; u, ma mmugren tifukal, ddan d ukyisen"
  25,73,"Wid, mara asen d smmektin issekniyen n Mass nnsen, ur d neggar tiâéegt ne$ tider$elt fellasen"
  25,74,"Wid iqqaôen: \"a Mass nne$! Err tilawin nne$, akked dderya nne$, d ssuâada n wallen. Err ane$ d wid inehhun wid ipêezziben"
  25,75,"Widak ad ppuoazin s t$uôfatin, ilmend n wayen ûebôen. Ad magren, dinna, azul, tifrat"
  25,76,"Dinna, ad wekkôen, d amkan amxalef i tnezdu$t d i$imi"
  25,77,"Ini: \"ur d Irezzu Mass iw, degwen, ma ur tnujem $uôeS. Ni$ tnekôem? Ad iu$al waya d ayen ilezmen"
  26,1,Ïsm
  26,2,Atnan issekniyen n Tezmamt ipbegginen
  26,3,"Ahat tqelqev iman ik, imi ur ppilin d lmumnin"
  26,4,"Ma ihwa ya£, ad asen d Nessers assekni seg igenni, ad îinzent, zdat es, tmegôav nnsen, s wannuz"
  26,5,"Ur ten id ippas usmekti amaynut, s$uô Uênin, mebla ma u$alen as d inekkaôen"
  26,6,"Ni$ skaddben. Ihi, ad asen d asen isallen, $ef wayen i$ef pmmaâliken"
  26,7,Day ur walan ara tamurt? Acêal i Nessenker degs n yal tayuga tukyist
  26,8,"Deg wayagi, s tidep, assekni. Tegwti degsen, ur llin d lmumnin"
  26,9,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,10,"Mi Issawel Mass ik, i Musa: \"ôuê s agdud imednas"
  26,11,agdud n Ferâun. Day ur ppezziben ara
  26,12,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Nek ugade$ ad iyi skiddben"
  26,13,"ad sekkwôen idmaren iw, ur ipserriê yiles iw. Ihi, Azen ar Haôun"
  26,14,U denbe$ $uôsen. Ugade$ ad iyi n$en
  26,15,"Inna: \"Xaîi, ôuêet s issekniyen nne£. Aql a£ yidwen, Nessemêas en. Ôö"
  26,16,"Öuêet ar Ferâun, tinem as: \"nekwni d amazan n Mass imavalen"
  26,17,"Seddu, yidne$, At Isôail"
  26,18,"Inna: \"day ur k nôebba ara $uône$, d llufan? U tesâaddav $uône$, iseggwasen di lâameô ik"
  26,19,"u txedmev igi txedmev. Keçç, seg ijehliyen"
  26,20,"Inna: \"xedme$ t asmi lli$ seg im$eôôqen"
  26,21,"Rewle$ segwen, mi kwen ugade$. Ifka yi Mass iw, ûûwab. Irra yi seg imazanen"
  26,22,"D l$it agi, i$ef a yi teppezzmev, i k ibbwin a pperrev, At Isôail, d aklan"
  26,23,"Inna Ferâun: \"d acu T Mass imavalen"
  26,24,"Inna: \"d Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, ma tetebbtem"
  26,25,"Inna i wi s d izzin: \"la tsellem"
  26,26,"Inna: \"Mass nnwen, u Mass n lejdud nnwen, imezwura"
  26,27,"Inna: \"s tidep, amazan nnwen id ippuceggâen $uôwen, d aôehbani"
  26,28,"Inna: \"Mass n ugmuv, utaram, akked wayen illan garasen, lemmer tefhimem"
  26,29,"Inna: \"ma tedmev Öebbi, ur nelli d nek, a k nerr ar lêebs"
  26,30,"Inna: \"i lemmer ad ak d awi$ ayen ipbegginen"
  26,31,"Inna: \"awi t id, ma d tidep ay tessawalev"
  26,32,"Iveggeô taâkwazt is, tu$al d azrem n ûûeê"
  26,33,"Issuffe$ ed afus is, d$a d amellal i imfeôoen"
  26,34,"Inna i imvebbôen i s d izzin: \"wagi, s tidep, d aseêêar amusnaw"
  26,35,"ib$a a kwen issuffe$, s ssêur is, seg wakal nnwen. D acu t lameô nnwen"
  26,36,"Nnan: \"sgani t, neppa akked gma s; azen ineccaden ar temdinin"
  26,37,ad ak d awin yal aseêêar amusnaw
  26,38,"Mlalen iseêêaren, di lweqt akked wass ipwassnen"
  26,39,"Nnan i imdanen: \"ma ad tenjemâam"
  26,40,"Ahat a neddu d iseêêaren, ma d nitni ara irebêen"
  26,41,"Mi d usan iseêêaren, nnan as i Ferâun: \"ma ad a$ tili teqdiât, ma nerbeê"
  26,42,"Inna: \"ih, d$a, kunwi, war ccekk, a ppu$alem seg iqôiben"
  26,43,"Inna yasen Musa: \"veggôet ayen ara tveggôem"
  26,44,"Veggôen imraren akked tâakwzin nnsen. Nnan: \"s tezmert n Ferâun, ard nekwni ara irebêen"
  26,45,Iveggeô Musa taâkwazt is. Apan tesseblaâ ayen id snulfan
  26,46,"Iseêêaren $lin, knan"
  26,47,"Nnan: \"numen s Mass imavalen"
  26,48,Mass n Musa akked Haôun
  26,49,"Inna: \"tumnem yiS, uqbel ma serrêe$ awen? Neppa, war ccekk, d ameqwôan nnwen i wen issêefven ssêur. A ppeéôem, ad awen gezme$ afus sya, avaô sya; a kwen ûûemôe$ akw $ef umidag"
  26,50,"Nnan: \"ulac u$ilif, acku ar Mass nne$, ara nezzi"
  26,51,"Ih, nessaram ad Isemmeê, Mass nne$, tuccva nne$ imi aql a$ d lmumnin imenza"
  26,52,"Nweêêa i Musa: \"ôôuê s ugdud iW, deg iv, acku a kwen in vefôen"
  26,53,Iuzen Ferâun ineccaden ar temdinin
  26,54,"wigi, s tidep, d arbaâ amejîuê"
  26,55,"u nitni, s tidep, sserfan a"
  26,56,"Nekwni, Neqquôa akken ma nella"
  26,57,"Ihi, Nessuffe$ iten id si tebêirin akked tliwa"
  26,58,"igerrujen, ixxamen ukyisen"
  26,59,"Akka, nweôôet yissen, At Isôail"
  26,60,Vefôen ten mi d inqeô yiîij
  26,61,"Mi mwalan irebbuyaâ, nnan imeddukwal n Musa: \"aql a$ a nepwalêeq"
  26,62,"Inna: \"xaîi! Mass iw, s tidep, yidi. Ad iyi Inhu"
  26,63,"Nweêêa i Musa: \"wwet ill s taâkwazt ik\"! Imfaôaq, yal loiha am udrar ameqwôaêan"
  26,64,Nessqeôb ed wiyav ar dinna
  26,65,"Nsellek Musa, akked wid akw iddan yides"
  26,66,Sinna ne$ôeq wiyav
  26,67,"Deg wayagi, s tidep, d assekni. Tegwti degsen ur uminen"
  26,68,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,69,Eêku yasen d tamacahup n Ibôahim
  26,70,"Mi inna i baba s akked ugdud is: \"d acu tâabdem"
  26,71,"Nnan: \"naâbed tiâancuôin, mazal a tent njjem"
  26,72,"Inna: \"day awen d sellent, ma tnujem"
  26,73,"Ne$ nefâant kwen, ne$ vuôôent kwen"
  26,74,"Nnan: \"xaîi, nufa d imezwura nne$, akka ay xeddmen"
  26,75,"Inna: \"day twalam ayen la tâabdem"
  26,76,kunwi akked lejdud nnwen imenza
  26,77,Nitni d icenga w. Siwa kan Mass imavalen
  26,78,iyi Ixelqen; Neppa iyi Inhan
  26,79,"Neppa iyi Icceççan, iyi Isswan"
  26,80,Neppa iyi Isseêluyen ma uvne
  26,81,"ara iyi In$en, sinna, ara iyi d Ssidren"
  26,82,"u, ôe$be$, d Win ara Isemmêen tuccva w, ass iqeîîiyen"
  26,83,"A Mass iw, £it iyi d, s ûûwab. Ssemlil iyi d iâaôviyen"
  26,84,"Err awal iw, d win n tidep, i ineggura"
  26,85,Err iyi si lweôôat n Loennet n ssuâada
  26,86,"Semmeê i baba. Neppa, s tidep, illa seg im$eôôqen"
  26,87,"Ur iyi Xezzu, ass n tnekra nnsen"
  26,88,"ass ideg ur infaâ wayla, ne$ derya"
  26,89,"siwa win iqublen Öebbi, s wul unûiê"
  26,90,"A d teppaé Loennet, ar wid ipêezziben"
  26,91,A d innunnet ujajiê ar im$eôôqen
  26,92,"Ad asen inin: \"anda ten wid tellam tâabdem"
  26,93,"war Öebbi? Day a kwen ssellken, ne$ ad ssellken iman nnsen"
  26,94,"Ad pwagren degs, nitni, akked wid i$elîen"
  26,95,"akked lâaskeô n Iblis, akken ma llan"
  26,96,"Ad inin; u nitni, degs, ppemqellaân"
  26,97,"s Öebbi, ar nella di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  26,98,mi kwen nessaâdel ar Mass imavalen
  26,99,D ibe$wviyen kan i a$ itelfen
  26,100,Ur nesâi imcafâen
  26,101,ne$ aêbib i $ iêemmlen
  26,102,"Lemmer ad as nales, a nili d lmumnin"
  26,103,"Deg wayagi, s tidep, assekni. Tegwti, degsen, ur uminen"
  26,104,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,105,Agdud n Nuê iskaddeb imazanen
  26,106,"Mi sen inna gmat sen Nuê: \"day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  26,107,"Nek, $uôwen, d amazan muman"
  26,108,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,109,"Ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiât, ilmend n waya. Ih, taqdiât iw, apan kan, ar Mass imavalen"
  26,110,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,111,"Nnan: \"day a k namen, mi ddan yidek imezwura n laâôuô"
  26,112,"Inna: \"ur éôi$ ayen xeddmen"
  26,113,"Aqeîîi nnsen $eô Mass iw kan, lemmer tessinem"
  26,114,"Ur swexxiôe$, nek, lmumnin"
  26,115,Nek d aneddaô kan ipbeginnen
  26,116,"Nnan: \"ma ur tfukkev, a Nuê, war ccekk, a ppepwaôeomev"
  26,117,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! S tidep, inkeô iyi ugdud iw"
  26,118,"Seyyi ferru gari yidsen. Sellek a$, nek, akked lmumnin i illan yidi"
  26,119,"Nsellek it, neppa, akked wid illan yides, di lbabuô iççuôen"
  26,120,"Sinna, deffir waya, Ne$ves wid igwran"
  26,121,"Deg wayagi, d assekni, war ccekk. Tegwti degsen, ur llin d lmumnin"
  26,122,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,123,Âad skaddben imazanen
  26,124,"Mi sen inna gmat sen Hud: \"day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  26,125,"Nek, $uôwen, d amazan muman"
  26,126,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,127,"Ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiât, ilmend n waya. Ih, taqdiât iw, apan kan, ar Mass imavalen"
  26,128,"Day a tbennum, di yal ti$ilt, assekni i tfukal nnwen"
  26,129,"La tepparam lebôuj, amar haat a pwekkôem"
  26,130,"Ma tewwtem, tekkatem s leqseê"
  26,131,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,132,Ëezzbet i Win i wen Ifkan ayen teéôam
  26,133,"Ifka yawen lmal, tarwa"
  26,134,"tibêirin, tiliwa"
  26,135,"Nek, ugade$ aâaqeb fellawen, ass ameqwôaêan"
  26,136,"Nnan: \"iaâdel $uône$ tnubav, ne$ ur tnubav"
  26,137,"Ih, ayagi, siwa d asnulfu imezwura"
  26,138,Ur nelli d wid ara ippuâaqben
  26,139,"Nekôen t. Nesqucc iten. Deg wayagi d assekni, war ccekk. Tegwti degsen, ur llin d lmumnin"
  26,140,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,141,Tamud skaddben imazanen
  26,142,"Mi sen inna gmat sen ÛüÜaliê: \"day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  26,143,"Nek, $uôwen, d amazan muman"
  26,144,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,145,"Ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiât, ilmend n waya. Ih, taqdiât iw, apan kan, ar Mass imavalen"
  26,146,"Day a kwen ooen, deg wayen illan dagi, testumnem"
  26,147,Di tebêirin akked tliwa
  26,148,"deg igran, tizdayin s ppemôa leqqaqen"
  26,149,"La tneoôem, d ccaîôin, ixxamen deg idurar"
  26,150,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,151,Ur ssemêaset i lameô iballa$en
  26,152,"i issefsaden di tmurt, ur pleqqimen"
  26,153,"Nnan: \"keçç, aql ak kan, seg iôehbaniyen"
  26,154,"Keçç d amdan kan, am nekwni. Awi d assekni, ma d tidep ay tessawalev"
  26,155,"Inna: \"tal$wemt agi, a ppessew deg wass is, kunwi a ppesswem deg wass nnwen"
  26,156,"£uôwat a p tevvuôem, mulac a kwen iwwet uâaqeb, deg wass abarar"
  26,157,"Gezmen as tigwecrar, gwran d di nndama"
  26,158,"Iwwet iten uâaqeb. Deg wayagi d assekni, war ccekk. Tegwti degsen, ur llin d lmumnin"
  26,159,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,160,Agdud n Luî iskaddeb imazanen
  26,161,"Mi sen inna gmat sen ÛüLuî: \"day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  26,162,"Nek, $uôwen, d amazan muman"
  26,163,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,164,"Ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiât, ilmend n waya. Ih, taqdiât iw, apan kan, ar Mass imavalen"
  26,165,Teppeddum ar ddkeô deg imavalen
  26,166,"Teooam tilawin i wen d Ixleq Mass nnwen? Ihi, kunwi d agdud izegren tilas"
  26,167,"Nnan: \"ma ur tfukkev, a Luî, a k nenfu"
  26,168,"Inna: \"nek, seg wid ikeôhen igiten nnwen"
  26,169,"A Mass iw, sellek iyi, nek akked twacult iw, seg igiten nnsen"
  26,170,"Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, meôôa"
  26,171,"siwa tam$aôt, ar wid igwran"
  26,172,"Sinna, Nessenger wiyav"
  26,173,Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur. I icmet ugeffur n wid ippunedôen
  26,174,"Deg wayagi d assekni, war ccekk. Tegwti degsen, ur llin d lmumnin"
  26,175,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,176,Agdud n At Teégi iskaddeb imazanen
  26,177,"Mi sen inna Cuâayeb: \"day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  26,178,"Nek, $uôwen, d amazan muman"
  26,179,"Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,180,"Ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiât, ilmend n waya. Ih, taqdiât iw, apan kan, ar Mass imavalen"
  26,181,Ktilet s lewqama; ur ppilit seg wid issenqasen
  26,182,Weznet s lmizan uwqim
  26,183,"Ur ccmatet i medden, ayla nnsen; ur ssexsaôet di tmurt s usefsed"
  26,184,"Ëezzbet i Win ikwen Ixelqen, kunwi akked isuta imenza"
  26,185,"Nnan: \"keçç, aql ak kan, seg iôehbaniyen"
  26,186,"Keçç, d amdan kan, am nekwni. Nêesb ik seg wid iskiddiben"
  26,187,"Sse$li d fellane$ igezman igenni, ma d tidep ay tessawalev"
  26,188,"Inna: \"Mass iw Iéôa, sennig wiyav, ayen txeddmem"
  26,189,"Skaddben t. Iwwet iten uâaqeb, deg wass n tillas. D aâaqeb, s tidep, n wass abarar"
  26,190,"Deg wayagi, d assekni, war ccekk. Tegwti degsen, ur llin d lmumnin"
  26,191,"Mass ik, s tidep, ar Neppa d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  26,192,"Ar wagi, war ccekk, d ayen id Issers Mass imavalen"
  26,193,"Irs ed, yides, ôôuê n laman"
  26,194,"ef wul ik, iwakken a ppiliv seg wid inedôen"
  26,195,s umeslay aâôab ipbegginen
  26,196,"Neppa, s tidep, deg Ihellilen imezwura"
  26,197,"Day ur illi ara d assekni i nitni, mi t ssnen imusnawen n At Isôail"
  26,198,"Lemmer it id Nessers, i yiwen seg ibeôôaniyen"
  26,199,"u i$ôa yasen t, ur ppamnen yis"
  26,200,"Akka, Nessawev it ar wulawen ibe$wviyen"
  26,201,"Ur ppamnen yis, alamma walan aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  26,202,"A ten id ias, deqzalla, nitni ur bnin"
  26,203,"Ad inin: \"amendeô ma neggani"
  26,204,Day êaren s aâaqeb nne£
  26,205,"Day ur twalav ara, N$at iten, d iseggwasen"
  26,206,"Sinna, iusa ten id wayen i sen ippuwaââden"
  26,207,Ula i sen d ibbwi wayen is stumnen
  26,208,"Ur Nesqucc tamdint, siwa tin isâan ineddaôen"
  26,209,i usmekti. Ur Nelli d imednas
  26,210,Ur d risen yides ccwaîen
  26,211,"Ur asen issefk, ur zmiren"
  26,212,"Nitni, s tidep, pwaâezlen $ef tmesliwt"
  26,213,"Ur nâaô, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven. Mulac a ppiliv seg wid ara ippuâaqben"
  26,214,Nabi llezm ik i k iqeôben mavi
  26,215,Ezger tacvaî ik $ef wi i k ivefôen si lmumnin
  26,216,"Ma âuûan k, ini: \"ur ppka$ deg wayen txeddmem"
  26,217,Ppkel $ef Uzmir Ipêunun
  26,218,I k Ipwalin mara tbeddev
  26,219,mara d tezziv ar wid iknan
  26,220,"Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  26,221,Ad awen mle$ anwi i$ef d prusun ccwaîen
  26,222,Prusun ed $ef yal akeddab idensen
  26,223,Ppaken tameééu$t. Tegwti degsen d ikeddaben
  26,224,"Imedyazen, îîafaôen ten im$eôôqen"
  26,225,"Day ur twalav ara, ar nitni, di yal ta$zut pmenîaôen"
  26,226,U nitni qqaôen ayen ur xeddmen
  26,227,"Kkes ed wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, id ismektayen aîas Öebbi, i irebêen mbaâd ma pwadensen. Ad éôen, wid idensen, tama anida ara ppin"
  27,1,"Ïs. Atnan issekniyen n Leqwôan, akked Tezmamt ipbegginen"
  27,2,D nnhaya u d abecceô i lmumnin
  27,3,"wid ibedden i téallit, ippaken zzakat, ipputebbten $ef laxeôt nnsen"
  27,4,"Ih, wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, Ncebbeê asen igiten nnsen, d$a ddebdeben"
  27,5,"Widak, fellasen aâaqeb ucmit mavi. Di laxeôt, d nitni ara ixesôen ugwar"
  27,6,"S tidep, keçç iusa k id Leqwôan, s$uô Bab n ûûwab, Amusnaw"
  27,7,"Mi inna Musa i twacult is: \"nek wala$ times, ad awen d awi$, segs, asali, ne$ ad awen d awi$ asafu iôeqqen, amar a ppesseêmum"
  27,8,"Mi ibbwev $uôes, ipwanced: \"ad iôqu wayen illan di tmes, akked wayen i as d izzin. Gedha s Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  27,9,"A Musa! Ih, Nek d Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"
  27,10,"Veggeô taâkwazt ik\"! Mi p iwala la tesseêôiîiw, amzun d azrem, ibren, ur iwexxeô. \"A Musa! Ur ppagwad! Ar $uôI, ih, ur ppagwaden imazanen"
  27,11,"siwa win idensen, sinna, iu$al iwqem, deffir tuccva. Nek, s tidep, Psemmiêe$, Pêunnu"
  27,12,"Ger afus ik di loib ik, a d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. Si tza issekniyen, i Ferâun akked ugdud is. Nitni, war ccekk, d agdud icemten"
  27,13,"Mi ten id usan issekniyen nne£, âinani, nnan: \"wagi iban d ssêur"
  27,14,"Ugin ten s ddens d pnefxa, u, deg iman nnsen, pputebbten. Wali, ihi, amek tevôa d ifessaden"
  27,15,"Ni$ Nefka tamusni i Dawed akked Sliman. Nnan: \"ccekôan i Öebbi, i a$ Ismenyafen i waîaû n yimdanen iumnen"
  27,16,"Sliman iwôet Dawed, u inna: \"a yimdanen! Nepwaselmed tutlayt n yifôax; ippunefk a$ si yal cci. Ayagi, s tidep, ard lfevl n ûûeê"
  27,17,"Pwajemmlen d, i Sliman, i²âsekôiwen is si leonun, imdanen, ifôax. Mdarraren"
  27,18,"Armi, mi bbwven ar te$zut n twevfin, tenna d tweîuft: \"a yaweîîuf, kecmemt ar ixxamen nnkwent, mulac, war ccekk, a kwent iéd Sliman, neppa akked iâsekôiwen is, ur faqen"
  27,19,"Icmumeê, ivûa, $ef wayen d tenna. Inna: \"a Mass iw! Err iyi ad snemmre$ l$it iK, is i $ T$atev, nek akked imawlan iw; ad xedme$ ise$ ara Tôaviv; Ssekcem iyi, s uêunu K, ar imdanen iK imaânen"
  27,20,"Issefqed ifôax, inna: \"acimi ur wala$ ara iççibib, day d l$ayeb"
  27,21,"War ccekk, ad sâaddi$ fellas aâaqeb uqsiê, ne$ a t zlu$, ne$ a d iawi tasebbiwt tubrizt"
  27,22,"Ur iâaîîel ara. Inna d: \"fehme$ ayen ur tefhimev. Usi$ d $uôek si Saba, s usali unûiê"
  27,23,"Ih, ufi$ en tameîîut d tagelliî nnsen. Ippunefk as si yal cci. £uôes asgeld abarar"
  27,24,"Ufi$ p in, neppat akked ugdud is, la kennun i yiîij, war Öebbi. Cciîan icebbeê asen igiten nnsen. Iveôf iten seg ubrid, d$a nitni ur pwanhan"
  27,25,"Acimi ur knan ara i Öebbi, id Issufu$en lesrar, di tmurt akked igenwan, i Iéôan ayen teppeffrem u ayen d tepberriêem"
  27,26,"Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan"
  27,27,"Inna: \"a néeô ma tessawlev d tidep, ne$ ma keçç seg ikeddaben"
  27,28,"Öuê s tebôap iw agi, veggeô asen p, sinna, wexxeô asen, wali acu ara d rren"
  27,29,"Tenna: \"a yimvebbôen, tepwaveggeô iyi d tebôap tukyist"
  27,30,"Ih, s$uô Sliman. Apan: s yisem n Öebbi Aênin Ipêunun"
  27,31,"Ur ssem$waôet ara iman nnwen $uôi, aset ed $uôi, d imvuâen"
  27,32,"Tenna: \"a yimvebbôen, fket ed ôôay nnwen af lameô iw. Ur pseyyi$ lameô, siwa garawen"
  27,33,"Nnan: \"nekwni d imawlan n tezmert, nesâa lemêella tuqsiêt. Lameô i kem. Muqel d acu ara d tseyyiv"
  27,34,"Tenna: \"s tidep, igeldan ssefsaden tamdint ara kecmen. Sdullun imdanen is lâali. Akka ay xeddmen"
  27,35,"Nek, ad asen azne$ tarzeft, ad aôou$ acu ara d awin imcegâan"
  27,36,"Mi tebbwev ar Sliman, inna: \"day ad iyi tâawnem s terkunt? Ayen i yi Ifka Öebbi, yif ayen i wen Ifka. D kunwi kan i ifeôêen, s terzeft nnwen"
  27,37,"U$al $uôsen. Ih, a nôuê $uôsen s lâaskeô, iwumi ur zmiren. A ten id nessuffe$, syenna, ndellen, d imejîuêen"
  27,38,"Inna: \"a yimvebbôen, anwa degwen, ara yi d iawin asgeld is, uqbel a yi d asen d imvuâen"
  27,39,"Aâfrit si leonun, inna d: \"ad ak t id awi$, uqbel ma tekkrev seg umekkan ik. I wayagi, war ccekk, nek d uzmir muman"
  27,40,"Inna d bab n tmusni si Tezmamt: \"nek ad ak t id awi$, uqbel a pfukkev asmeômec\". Mi t iwala irs ed $uôes, inna: \"wagi si lfevl n Mass iw, ad iyi ijeôôeb ma ad snemmre$, ne$ ma ad jehle$. Win isnemmren, isnemmer kan i iman is. Win ijehl, ihi, Mass iw d Asâay, d Ukyis"
  27,41,"Inna: \"bedlet as udem usgeld is, a néeô ma tepwanha, ne$ haap seg wid ur nepwanha"
  27,42,"Mi d tusa, nnan as: \"day am wagi, usgeld inem\"? Terra d: \"amzun d neppa\". \"Tusa ya$ d tmusni, uqbel neppat, nuzen"
  27,43,"Isôuê ip wayen tunez, war Öebbi. Tella, s tidep, seg ugdud ijehliyen"
  27,44,"Nnan as: \"ekcem ar lbeôo\"! Mi t twala, t$il degs aman; tesban ed ifadden is. Inna: \"s tidep, d lbeôo ulelluc imzin\". Tenna: \"a Mass iw! Ih, dense$ iman iw. Akked Sliman, unze$ aS i Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  27,45,"Ni$ Nuzen ed, i Tamud, gmat sen Üaliê: \"âabdet Öebbi\"! Maca, rran snat n trebbuya$, ppemnamarent"
  27,46,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acimi tep$awalem ar tucmip, uqbel ise$? Lemmer a ppeste$fôem Öebbi, ahat aêunu fellawen"
  27,47,"Nnan: \"tkeêêesev a$, keçç akked wi iddan yidek\". Inna: \"lfal nnwen ar Öebbi, u kunwi d agdud ara ippuhewwlen"
  27,48,"Llan, di temdint, tza iterrasen i issefsaden di tmurt, ur pleqqimen"
  27,49,"Nnan: \"yyaw a nemmesgal s Öebbi, ard a neévem deg iv fellas, neppa akked twacult is. Sinna, a nini i bab is: ur nelli d inagan n tmen$iwt n tawacult is. Ih, nekwni, d imawlan n tidep"
  27,50,"Undin ticeôkep, Nundi ticeôkep, nitni ur faqen"
  27,51,"Wali amek tevôa di tceôkep nnsen. Nen$ed iten, nitni, akked ugdud nnsen, meôôa"
  27,52,"Atnan hudden ixxamen nnsen, ilmend n ddens nnsen. Deg wayagi, war ccekk, assekni i ugdud issnen"
  27,53,Nsellek wid iumnen u llan pêezziben
  27,54,"I Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: \"teppeddum ar wayen n dir, u kunwi tepwalim"
  27,55,"Ih, kunwi teppeddum ar irgazen, teb$am ten, war tilawin. Ih, kunwi d agdud ur nessin"